com.simiacryptus.mindseye.network

Interface DAGNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Serializable

    public interface DAGNode
extends Serializable
    This is a logical node used within a network graph definition. It is associated with a NNLayer WITHOUT a 1:1 relation assumtion; i.e. the same logical layer CAN be used twice in the same graph. Also, the layer assigned to a node can be updated, which can be useful for adding/removing instrumentation wrappers.
